---
description: Go conventions (service-local)
globs: "**/*.go"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Go

- Domain: `internal/<service>/` (identity: model/repository/service)
- Transport: `internal/app/api/<service>/`
- Adapters: `internal/adapter/`
- Wiring: `cmd/<service>/app/run.go` only
- `make lint` / `make test` from service root
